    Package Description
    concentrationSite
    This package contains the Concentration Site Monitor and all other interfaces to the entities to access to the methods, for example, IMasterThief is the Master Thief interface of the Concentration Site Instance.

    Main package, it contains the constants file and the definition of the entities: Master Thief and Ordinary Thief.
